00:17:07.569 --> 00:17:09.760 align:middle line:84%
And so you're always in
stress with the universe.

00:17:09.760 --> 00:17:10.900 align:middle line:90%
That's not enlightenment.

00:17:10.900 --> 00:17:13.660 align:middle line:84%
